Package: linux-33-image-@abiname@@localversion@
Provides: linux-33-image, linux-33-modules-@abiname@@localversion@
Pre-Depends: debconf | debconf-2.0
Depends: kmod | module-init-tools (>= 3.16), ${misc:Depends}
Conflicts: r8168-dkms
Recommends: firmware-linux-33-free (>= 3~)
Suggests: linux-33-doc-@version@
Description: Linux @upstreamversion@ for @class@
 The Linux kernel @upstreamversion@ and modules for use on @longclass@.

Package: linux-33-image@localversion@
Section: metapackages
Priority: extra
Depends: linux-33-image-@abiname@@localversion@ (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: linux-33-headers@localversion@ (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Linux image for siduction on @class@
 This metapackage depends on the latest binary image for Linux kernel on
 @longclass@ machines for siduction.

Package: linux-33-headers@localversion@
Section: metapackages
Priority: extra
Depends: linux-33-headers-@abiname@@localversion@ (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Linux header for siduction on @class@
 This metapackage depends on the latest binary image for Linux kernel on
 @longclass@ machines for siduction.


